{"id":"FH-0489","name":"Movimento Armorial","type":"evento","subtype":"Movimento Artistico","description":"O movimento armorial, surgido na década de 70 no Brasil, foi uma vertente artístico-cultural de valorização das artes populares nordestinas. O objetivo central era criar uma arte brasileira singular baseada nas raízes populares. Idealizado pelo escritor paraibano Ariano Suassuna, essa manifestação abrangeu a literatura, música, dança, teatro, artes plásticas, arquitetura, cinema, etc.","de":"The movimento armorial, which emerged in Brazil in the 1970s, was an artistic-cultural current that valued the popular arts of the Northeast. Its central aim was to create a singular Brazilian art rooted in popular traditions. Conceived by the Paraíba-born writer Ariano Suassuna, this movement encompassed literature, music, dance, theatre, visual arts, architecture, cinema, and so on.","period":"","reference_location":"","municipality":"Pernambuco","neighborhood":"","image":"","aliases":[],"sources":[{"id":"FT-0001","title":"https://antonioaurel.github.io/data/data-visualization/recife-history-connections/pages/sources.html","source_type":"url","author":"","year":"","url":"https://antonioaurel.github.io/data/data-visualization/recife-history-connections/pages/sources.html","notes":""}],"edges":[{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0014","target_name":"Antônio Madureira","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0015","target_name":"Antônio Nóbrega","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0017","target_name":"Ariano Suassuna","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"target_id":"LC-0517","target_name":"Casa Armorial","target_type":"local","type":"local","strength":1},{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0080","target_name":"Francisco Brennand","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0090","target_name":"Gilvan Samico","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"tar